      <title>杰罗姆·鲍威尔的转变推动华尔街股市势不可挡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/jerome-powell-s-pivot-fuels-an-all-conquering-wall-street-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰罗姆·鲍威尔发出了迄今为止最果断的信号，表明他的抗通胀任务已经完成，这有助于恢复市场秩序。仅在三周前，市场还陷入了自疫情以来最严重的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/jerome-powell-s-pivot-fuels-an-all-conquering-wall-street-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 20:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
