      <title>爱尔兰信用评级因公共财政和经济增长前景而上调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/ireland-credit-rating-raised-by-scope-on-public-finances-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Scope Ratings 将爱尔兰的信用评级上调了一个等级，因为该国拥有强劲的公共财政和强劲的经济增长。]]></description>
